{"tid":32554,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★［富戶政策?］仆街了！大戶下周料 搶樓 掃舖!","createTime":"2016-12-10T08:41:46.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-10T13:49:28.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"23c4b11437b1fbf46cd8e8c3cbbf3ef01a95d641","tid":32554,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T08:41:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20161210/00176_035.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20161210%2F00176_035.html&d=O%2FRWeA2pu0Ji7bc9PnC4oAT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=7fcb72bb\" target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20161210/00176_035.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n北角住宅屋苑和富中心有逾千方呎大單位業主，原先以一千八百萬元放盤，亦即時封盤不賣，屯門上車屋苑邁亞美海灣亦有兩房單位業主封盤，兩位業主表明睇好後市；更有資深舖市投資者追價三十五萬元搶購新界舖位。業界人士指出，市民對樓市信心轉強，預期二手樓反價、封盤陸續增加。據財經界可靠消息指，投資界大戶周一將殺入股市及樓市，尤其會積極買住宅及掃舖位。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5730d1ac958141c1c90934b13f305eb32f2250ad","tid":32554,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T08:44:06.000Z","msg":"咁快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n明年十月才開始實施，仲要2018年4月左右才開始申報"},{"pid":"b4af0bfbb7024ab0e6c31f5457ec1b28e6ddb91e","tid":32554,"uid":60052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T08:47:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n明年十月才開始實施，仲要2018年4月左右才開始申報</blockquote><br />\n唔講下個市邊有得炒"},{"pid":"7e23ea89ff9a31d63a6f59fcd167ea5b982a048c","tid":32554,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T08:49:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n明年十月才開始實施，仲要2018年4月左右才開始申報</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n而且呢個係689連任政策，佢都唔做，分分鐘無限期擱置<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0e9ff1a5a0688b2369e88cf57f24dc60c4d91a9","tid":32554,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T11:06:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1128c3dc4ae075fbf6439ba361b483848f12cd1e","tid":32554,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T13:49:28.000Z","msg":"lm"}]}